Trans - Lux Corp buys scoreboard sign segment . Trans - Lux Corp said on Thursday that its subsidiary had aquired the catalog and custom scoreboard sign business segment of Fairtron Corp , to enable it to reach broader markets . The company did not say how much the acquisition was worth , but reported that revenues for the latest fiscal year for the catalog scoreboard business , excluding revenues of the custom business , were about $ 8 . 5 million . " The catalog scoreboard business primarily serves college and high school sports facilities and is a natural follow - up to the company ' s previous acquisitions , " said Trans - Lux chief executive Victor Liss . Trans - Lux manufactures and services real - time electronic information displays . 
